snippet.title: With All My Heart - Inspirational Love Song by Lifebreakthrough
snippet.description:
WITH ALL MY HEART (Lyrics)
Lifebreakthrough

Every now and then and for eternity
God bless the day when He gave me you
Every now and then and for a lifetime
I bless this day and cherish your faith in me

I'm gonna pray with you, walk with you, stay with you until the end
I'm gonna laugh with you, cry with you, breathe with you all my days
The road may be rough, vague and dark, bleak and tough
I promise to cherish you with all my heart

In all my dreams, my earnest hope
I wish you well every minute, every day
In all my dreams, my dearest friend
May the Lord protect you in every way

I'm gonna pray with you, walk with you, stay with you until the end
I'm gonna laugh with you, cry with you, breathe with you all my days
The road may be rough, vague and dark, bleak and tough
I promise to cherish you with all my heart

I'm gonna pray with you, walk with you, stay with you until the end
I'm gonna laugh with you, cry with you, breathe with you all my days
The road may be rough, vague and dark, bleak and tough
I promise to cherish you with all my heart

snippet.title: At The Cross - Beautiful Country Gospel Song by Lifebreakthrough
snippet.description:
https://lifebreakthroughmusic.com/
AT THE CROSS
Songwriter: Hubert Dapliyan
 
At the Cross, I saw my reflection
At the Cross, I saw the wickedness in me
At the Cross, I saw my arrogance
At the Cross, I saw amazing grace
 
At the Cross, I saw You crying
At the Cross, I saw You pray for me
At the Cross, I saw Your humble heart
At the Cross, I saw amazing grace
 
You love me more than I am
You love me in spite of my sinful ways
You love me for who I am
You love me in spite of my selfish ways
 
At the Cross, I saw salvation
At the Cross, I saw Your forgiveness to me
At the Cross, I saw the beauty of faith
At the Cross, I saw amazing grace
 
You love me more than I am
You love me in spite of my sinful ways
You love me for who I am
You love me in spite of my selfish ways
 
You love me in spite of my selfish ways
